'''卡梅隆·杰罗梅'''（{{lang-en|'''Cameron Zishan Jerome'''}}，{{bd|1986年|10月14日|||J}}）[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]職業足球員，司職[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]，現效力於[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[卢顿足球俱乐部|盧頓]]。

==生平==
===球會===
謝路美於本地球隊Westend Juniors開始足球訓練，後來轉至[[哈德斯菲爾德足球俱樂部|哈德斯菲爾德]]，亦曾於[[格林斯比镇足球俱乐部|甘士比]]和[[錫周三|錫周三]]接受足球訓練<ref>{{cite web | title=Jerome grateful to Wilkinson | work=Wales at Heart | url=http://www.walesatheart.com/Sport/February%202005/010205-05.htm | accessdate=2006-09-21 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060523103755/http://walesatheart.com/Sport/February%202005/010205-05.htm | archivedate=2006-05-23 }}</ref>。2003年，謝路美在[[英超|英超]]球隊[[米杜士堡足球會|米杜士堡]]踢球，後來被球隊放棄，在[[英冠|英冠]]球隊[[卡迪夫城足球俱樂部|卡迪夫城]]獲得合約，得以繼續足球事業，更被[[BBC|BBC]]形容為「卡迪夫城明日之星」，謝路美於2004-05賽季上陣32場射入7球，2005-06賽季更射入20球成為卡迪夫城的首席射手。因此獲[[伯明翰城足球俱樂部|伯明翰城]]青睞。

2006年5月31日，謝路美通過體檢正式與[[伯明翰城足球俱樂部|伯明翰城]]簽約，轉會費350萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Birmingham complete Jerome deal |publisher=BBC Sport |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/5028786.stm |date=2006-05-31 |accessdate=2006-09-21 |archive-date=2007-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070107044807/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/5028786.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[錫菲聯|錫菲聯]]、[[西布朗|西布朗]]、[[诺里奇城足球俱乐部|诺里奇城]]亦曾表示對謝路美有興趣。2006年9月12日，謝路美對[[昆士柏流浪|昆士柏流浪]]為伯明翰城射入首個入球。謝路美助伯明翰城升上英超，於2007年8月25日對[[德比郡足球俱樂部|打比郡]]僅32秒即射入首個英超入球，助伯明翰贏得[[2007年至2008年英格蘭超級聯賽|該季]]首場英超賽事<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/6952880.stm |title=Derby 1-2 Birmingham |author=May, John |publisher=BBC |date=2007-08-25 |accessdate=2007-12-04 |archive-date=2009-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090501002203/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/6952880.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{efn|Soccerbase's stats for the match between Derby County and Birmingham City on 9 March 2007 fail to include appearances by substitutes for either side, one of whom was Jerome.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/matches/results.sd?date=2007-03-09 |title=Results & Matches on: Fri, 9 Mar 2007 |work=Soccerbase |publisher=Centurycomm |accessdate=2011-05-13 |archive-date=2018-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180117190801/http://www.soccerbase.com/matches/results.sd?date=2007-03-09 |dead-url=no }} Click on match score for team details.</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/6415039.stm |title=Birmingham 1–0 Derby |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2007-03-09 |accessdate=2010-08-24 |archive-date=2007-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070319235424/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/6415039.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref> Additionally, the Dubious Goals Panel awarded Jerome a goal against Burnley on 1 May 2010,<ref name=DubiousGoal>{{cite web |url=http://www.premierleague.com/page/Headlines/0,,12306~2059030,00.html |title=Dubious goals |publisher=Premier League |date=2010-05-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100528093739/http://www.premierleague.com/page/Headlines/0%2C%2C12306~2059030%2C00.html |archivedate=2010-05-28 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2018-01-18 }}</ref> originally given as a Brian Jensen own goal, bringing his total of League goals for the 2009–10 season to 11.<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bcfc.com/page/News/NewsDetail/0,,10412~2059057,00.html |title=Extra Goal For Jerome! |publisher=Birmingham City F.C. |date=2010-05-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100528171446/http://www.bcfc.com/page/News/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10412~2059057%2C00.html |archivedate=2010-05-28 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2018-01-18 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/matches/results.sd?date=2010-05-01 |title=Results & Matches on: Sat, 1 May 2010 |work=Soccerbase |publisher=Centurycomm |accessdate=2011-05-13 |archive-date=2017-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170705161531/http://www.soccerbase.com/matches/results.sd?date=2010-05-01 |dead-url=no }} Click on "i" for goalscorer details.</ref> Until and unless they correct the figures, he should have one more League appearance and one more League goal for Birmingham than given on his Soccerbase page, i.e. his League totals for his career at Birmingham should be 181 appearances and 37 goals.<ref name=StokeProfile>{{cite news |url=http://www.stokecityfc.com/page/ProfilesDetail/0,,10310~30567,00.html |title=Cameron Jerome |publisher=Stoke City F.C. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110925174920/http://www.stokecityfc.com/page/ProfilesDetail/0%2C%2C10310~30567%2C00.html |archivedate=2011-09-25 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2018-01-18 }}</ref>|name=WrongStats}}

2011年謝路美隨同伯明翰降班[[英冠|英冠]]，於[[2011年至2012年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|新球季]]為球隊以後補身上陣1場後，在8月31日[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]關閉前一天轉投[[英超|英超]]球會[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]，簽約四年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14733502.stm |title=Cameron Jerome moves from Birmingham to Stoke |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-08-31 |accessdate=2011-09-02 |archive-date=2011-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110831171237/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14733502.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年9月3日於[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]關閉前被借用到[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宮]]一整個球季<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/23939888 |title=Crystal Palace sign Stoke striker Cameron Jerome on loan |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2013-09-03 |accessdate=2014-08-24 |archive-date=2015-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150322113248/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/23939888 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年8月20日，謝路美轉投剛降班[[英冠|英冠]]的[[诺里奇城足球俱乐部|诺里奇城]]，簽約三年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28869774 |title=Norwich City sign Carlos Cuellar and Cameron Jerome |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2014-08-20 |accessdate=2014-08-24 |archive-date=2015-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414141402/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28869774 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===國家隊===
謝路美是[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊]]成員，可參加2009年的[[歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|歐洲U-21足球錦標賽]]。

